{"tid":1314691,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大圍媽咪雞蛋仔","createTime":"2019-07-14T09:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T13:29:43.000Z","uid":107162,"like":8,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"00abbc23f3d4c7eeb6dac5416e10647e6a00536a","tid":1314691,"uid":107162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T09:59:33.000Z","msg":"今日朋友諗住喺大圍買個小食當lunch<br />\n見到有雞蛋仔就諗住仆去食啦<br />\n點知聽到入面啲職員指住出面遊行人士話<br />\n「好多暴徒啊.. 好驚啊..」<br />\n又指住啲拎旗嘅人話<br />\n「咪又係用埋啲淘寶貨」<br />\n仲好似講咗句「香港好多間諜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然聽對話佢地應該係普通職員<br />\n但係都請大家罷食大圍火車站附近嘅媽咪雞蛋仔<br />\n唔洗佢地咁撚辛苦整野俾暴徒食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要一底咁撚貴.. 夠食2個華御結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0040874bd9b145626fba9abb76daecc01125a16d","tid":1314691,"uid":50658,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T10:01:07.000Z","msg":"看圖作文都算<br />\n連圖都冇"},{"pid":"797e676dbf25df73ad461bc821b4972d290cd2f4","tid":1314691,"uid":211305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"d職員未又係新移民"},{"pid":"dfbfbcd1a4e23ba004c4d1ac4fe5171f2eb62e56","tid":1314691,"uid":178589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"咁貴 比都唔食！"},{"pid":"cff8080aa1d42195ca78461ee4f7c9c9e5507473","tid":1314691,"uid":107162,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0040874bd9b145626fba9abb76daecc01125a16d","tid":1314691,"uid":50658,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T10:01:07.000Z","msg":"看圖作文都算<br />\n連圖都冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T10:06:35.000Z","msg":"sor 唔識po圖<br />\n一路都係cd rom<br />\n今次太嬲先上黎開po<br />\n我真係有行過去的.. 試po圖 <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/14/RhieSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.